short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Populate the username on AgentNet web site

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The web site AgentNet has the username marked as Autocomplete = off.  Even the AutoComplete On! extension isn't ideal so this extension lets the user specify the username to inject into the username field.
